    "For example, studies show that during Covid eyesight among young children worsened in Hong Kong (Ho, 2023).",
    "However, there are experts that disagree with these claims and argue that the evidence for long term effects are not established (NCT).",
    "There are other arguments to say that using electronic devices is acceptable or even good for children.",
    "For instance, there is more and more work at school from the primary level that is on devices.",
    "Students in the future will probably have to complete work on computers or tablets more than ever, meaning students that do not use these devices may struggle in the adult world or workforce."
